definition.text: Superalgos visual interface features hundreds of icons and many more icons are required with each release, as new functionality is rolled out. Designing icons is a great way to leave your mark, as it puts your work directly in front of every user!

paragraphs.text: The original set of icons is a web design pack made by Freepik and is available at:
The rest of the series is inspired in the design style developed for the original set.
